After entering the planet's atmosphere, Meteara took her speed down in 
order to keep the landscape intact when she would land. She was 
approaching the position of Kup and Sunhawk, and she hoped she was not 
too late.

After a few minutes, she was visible to both of them, but she stood 
hovering high in the air. Her arrival, though had made much noise, so 
she was not totally unannounced.
